│ of CmpXZ or CmpYZ is known and swaps so CmpXZ is known.\n- For ordered        │
│ predicates, it decides outcomes based on whether the min/max predicate        │
│ direction matches the comparison predicate (IsSame) and whether X compares    │
│ before or after Z.\n\nIn our case, the decision path taken in the emitted log │
